<div class="container">
    <h1>Non-Vegetarian Diet Plan for Weight Gain</h1>

    <h2>General Guidelines</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Caloric Surplus: Aim for 300-500 extra calories daily.</li>
        <li>Frequent Meals: Eat 5-6 smaller meals/snacks throughout the day.</li>
        <li>Nutrient-Dense Foods: Focus on whole, high-calorie foods.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sample Meal Plan</h2>

    <h3>Breakfast</h3>
    <p>Scrambled eggs (3-4 eggs) with cheese and spinach</p>
    <p>Whole grain toast with butter</p>
    <p>A banana or an avocado</p>

    <h3>Morning Snack</h3>
    <p>Greek yogurt with honey and a handful of granola</p>

    <h3>Lunch</h3>
    <p>Grilled chicken breast with quinoa and roasted vegetables (zucchini, bell peppers)</p>
    <p>A side salad with olive oil dressing</p>

    <h3>Afternoon Snack</h3>
    <p>Tuna salad on whole grain crackers</p>

    <h3>Dinner</h3>
    <p>Baked salmon with brown rice and steamed broccoli</p>
    <p>A sweet potato with butter</p>

    <h3>Evening Snack</h3>
    <p>Cottage cheese with pineapple or berries</p>
</div>

